{"tid":1718373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有險可守】前終審法院法官，關心政府唔夠人手做檢控","createTime":"2019-11-13T23:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T16:08:28.000Z","uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5f553e9048ef62153041ac798426297b663aaaa9","tid":1718373,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T23:46:12.000Z","msg":"前終審法院常任法官烈顯倫出席無綫電視節目後表示：<br />\n<br />\n1. 認為法庭應該增加人手，處理大量額外案件，又相信律政司已經聘請很多人負責檢控。<br />\n<br />\n2. 他稱，示威者的行為已是違法，「你嘅意圖係第一個問題，有無破壞法律呢？就一定有。好深（嚴重）嘅法律問題添啦」<br />\n<br />\n3. 強調不能以言語減低嚴重犯法的後果。<br />\n<br />\n4. 對於有北京干預黃之峰參選，烈顯倫指說法「笑死人」。他反問「黃之鋒係邊個呀？香港都係一粒嘢，啲咁大。真係笑死人，北京政府會控制黃之鋒喺香港做嘢真係笑話」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個話終院D官未紅？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/289980/【移交逃犯修例】烈顯倫：法庭應增人手處理大量/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F289980%2F%E3%80%90%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%83%88%E9%A1%AF%E5%80%AB%EF%BC%9A%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E6%87%89%E5%A2%9E%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%2F&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=61d39b5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/289980/【移交逃犯修例】烈顯倫：法庭應增人手處理大量/</a>"},{"pid":"c2954c9414085dc68e8a6644613de9b051befbd3","tid":1718373,"uid":202464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T23:49:21.000Z","msg":"有晒政治立場，仲講咩公平公正"},{"pid":"2039ac4855bde404af798ea6229a76fb8463d17f","tid":1718373,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T23:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cc2647ee7520eba6a6d346e3818ef41dfee0bf","tid":1718373,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T23:56:51.000Z","msg":"有險可守"},{"pid":"de9c26c3b5858342555118b3dcc26573106ff973","tid":1718373,"uid":2024